Description_lang: Any player flying through the essence of the Emerald Dream empowers all players, increasing their damage done by $s1% and increasing their healing and absorb effects done by $s4%. This effect stacks and lasts until $@spellname424140 finishes casting or is interrupted.The consumed essence leaves behind $@spellname421884.
